      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and pampered like a member of the family. Seriously, it\u2019s in flawless shape\u2014looks and drives exactly like it did the day it rolled off the lot! If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one. Come take it for a spin, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
