      "description": "This vehicle is a true masterpiece of engineering and care, presented in a state that can only be described as showroom-fresh. Every inch of the exterior gleams with a deep, mirror-like finish, free of even the slightest swirl marks or stone chips. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, and all original technology functions with surgical precision. This car has been garage-kept since day one, never seeing inclement weather, and its service history is documented with obsessive detail. Mechanically, it is indistinguishable from the day it rolled off the assembly line. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the opportunity you have been waiting for.",
